title: 'OAI-compatible provider: reasoning_content field + tag-based thinking styles'
---
Add `oai_thinking_style: string` to runtime_config.ml provider_config (default "none"); update config_loader.ml JSON parser.

Implement in provider.ml OAI-compatible complete_stream:

'reasoning_content' style:
- Check choices[0].delta.reasoning_content field in each stream chunk
- If non-null/non-empty: emit ThinkingDelta
- Normal choices[0].delta.content continues to emit Delta

'tags' style:
- State machine: Normal | InThinking
- Buffer = last 8 chars (length of "</think>") for split-chunk detection
- On "<think>": switch to InThinking, don't emit delimiter
- On "</think>": switch to Normal, don't emit delimiter
- Normal state: emit Delta; InThinking state: emit ThinkingDelta

Edge cases to handle:
- Tag split across two chunks (e.g., "<thi" + "nk>")
- Nested angle brackets that aren't think tags
- Provider sends both reasoning_content and content in same chunk

Acceptance criteria:
- Unit tests for 'reasoning_content' style (with and without field present)
- Unit tests for 'tags' style: normal, split-chunk at various positions, consecutive tags
- `make test` passes